/#
   Provides information about a regulator or other supervisory body that an organization is registered with.
 #/
record FpML5.transparency.SupervisorRegistration {
  # The regulator or other supervisory body the organization is registered with (e.g. SEC).
  supervisoryBody : string

  # The ID assigned by the regulator (e.g. SEC's Central Index Key).
  registrationNumber : string?

}

supervisoryBody.Doc: The regulator or other supervisory body the organization is registered with (e.g. SEC).
supervisoryBody.Name: supervisoryBody

registrationNumber.Doc: The ID assigned by the regulator (e.g. SEC's Central Index Key).
registrationNumber.Name: registrationNumber
